org.eclipse.viatra.dse.objectives.impl

Class ModelQueriesHardObjective

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.viatra.dse.objectives.impl.BaseObjective
      • org.eclipse.viatra.dse.objectives.impl.ModelQueriesHardObjective
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IObjective
    Deprecated. 
    Use ConstraintsObjective instead.

    @Deprecated
public class ModelQueriesHardObjective
extends BaseObjective
    This hard objective collects a list of VIATRA Query patterns and checks if any of them has a match on a solution (trajectoy). It is unsatisfied if any of them has a match returning 0 or it is satisfied if none of them has a match returning 1.
